    hospital services.
 
Hastings Memorial Hospital - Intensive Care Unit
  - Mechanical and air conditioning services
 
Nelson Hospital - New Laundry, Boilerplant and Workshops
  - Laundry process flow, equipment selection, mechanical and electrical
    services, additional boilerplant and new workshop M. and E. Services.
 
North Canterbury Hospital Board - Christchurch Hospital
  - New Kitchen/Dining Room Block - Mechanical and ventilation services.
 
